title: Learn Finnish - Finnish Learning Pack 2014
description:
Yet another collection of books to learn Finnish, this one is quite smaller in size as compared to the previous packs(the video courses are not included here). The scan quality of most of the courses, however, is excellent. Since many courses are in DjVu format, WinDjView-2.0.2-Setup is included in the torrent. The book list is available in the first file of the torrent. I have uploaded over 3 TB of the previous torrent, The Ultimate Finnish Language Learning Pack (2013), but still not many continue to seed it, the size is quite large, and Finnish is not a major world language. This pack is much smaller (4.51 GB) and could survive longer, please try to seed it as much as you can!

Contents:

01-10 Courses for beginners in English and Finnish
11-17 Courses for beginners in Russian
18-26 Intermediate level Courses in Finnish and Spoken Finnish
27-34 Courses for school children in Russian
35-42 Conversational Manuals, phrasebooks, dictionaries, vocabulary
43-56 Grammar, workbooks
57-69 Graded readers, adapted texts, Folk Tales, Harry Potter
70-73 Country guides
74 Intermediate level course in Russian

The torrent files of the Finnish films and music collections are included in this pack, I try to seed them as well.
